          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The second type of experiment measured the angular",
                "distribution for formation of the 016 fragments in",
                "the ground state or with 6-7 MeV of excitation",
                "energy. For this measurement the angle-defining",
                "detector subtended 1.8 degree in the reaction plane,",
                "while the recoil collecting detector subtended 3.1-4.5",
                "degrees. Since the angle between the two oxygen",
                "fragments is approximately 1 degree greater for 7 MeV",
                "of excitation energy than for 6 MeV of excitation",
                "energy, as many as 40% of the partners formed with 7",
                "MeV of excitation energy may not have been detected",
                "because the angle between the detectors was set to",
                "correspond to that expected for formation of the",
                "oxygen fragments with 6 MeV of excitation energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
